{"h57755197g6ae0g424bgbb61g071aac586e22": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "c9fd7385-b26f-3caa-d9f8-3427ce5c67ed"], "hd01745a7g7316g4412gae7cg405f7697d3ec": ["Do you know why any of us were taken?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "ebe176d1-3472-0763-3f4b-1e947e4d7711"], "hb02c05bdgc834g4588g9247g9086993dd890": ["No...Took everyone...Peasants...Lords...Took them all... ", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "d7461db7-c534-d053-2e58-ad74f7d4f4ee"], "ha23cfc1cgf804g448dgb690g4179e10907f9": ["They put something in my eye too. Can we get rid of it?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "8447086c-b6c2-f839-5142-7e43ae116e15"], "h283e09adg7444g4ec3ga565g1522ebf52422": ["Find healer...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "f94044e0-6556-998e-ad54-f2a9de89d595"], "hc400f132gf2f8g4cfdg8ea4gd853f496fcb6": ["... or die... it'll leave...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "504194c4-7a3f-039d-2f37-6253c5cd847e"], "hae5722acg1e23g41b2g866ag77b5708bcb7f": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "e6c2a8ea-5c3b-b060-d2ed-c274be696e19"], "hbf4615b7g2308g4af3g9a3bg79a66567f183": ["Francis...merchant...selling pottery...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "fd721a15-8a90-82a8-35ba-a740abc55fa1"], "hae4be002ga6a6g4043g8c49g568937d63bbd": ["What happened to you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "9b9bad78-23b8-27af-b57d-a39c95cdcdda"], "he355d30bgdda1g411dg887dg6d58bb37dcfd": ["Guiding my cart...shadow fell...tentacle grabbed me...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "a3e3c287-1144-be92-8ebd-3230488bca2f"], "h4bf2bbfag52ffg41d7gb0c7g6d39518eb663": ["Took me here...put something in my eye...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "3f96925e-6af2-42e3-4bb0-46c5443c569e"], "hd0210faeg1ed9g4bbcg971eg1bfa0c194247": ["How did you die?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "bf168d2f-d7f7-ce5b-6314-b5322c7cc891"], "h7d005820gb188g4f7cg8fc1gd6bafcd4c068": ["Fire...screaming... then <i>crunch</i>. Nothing...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "d65eca42-cfe6-d55b-ca9e-ce724bf2a2ba"], "h7f1b651bg719fg4530ga94fg0d1747901dac": ["Do you have anything valuable?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "a6df80f6-f9a1-e758-1cca-8bbbc61b59de"], "h0eca71cegbf0eg48edg87e1g06ff14a586a1": ["They took me...took everything...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "3ac6acef-3335-73f4-8ffd-856ace92d916"], "hacd58c61gae6ag47b4gb43fg62d56bc58527": ["Are there any rites you'd like performed over your body?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "35839438-eee3-3ac0-f4b4-d9e501133b16"], "h6459f45bgbabbg43a6gaee3g14b162e1a8d7": ["Not from your cursed god...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "97e86ef5-e6f9-b0b6-631f-c0805a4e1c4d"], "h8d3dab08g6f34g42f3g950ag6eb0a9111080": ["Too late now...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "97e86ef5-e6f9-b0b6-631f-c0805a4e1c4d"], "h61245ab2g31d2g4a3dg9479gec22b1df3354": ["I could sing a song to remember you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "1c8af136-e122-64f6-4229-0bc71749ec9a"], "hea944fa1g0d97g4ee9g8d1fge0f153fe43f1": ["Doesn't matter...nothing matters...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "0481be5d-7651-6037-5974-c85a08e3fe60"], "h8d3e0c29gebedg4503g9592g2ad28ce2ac4e": ["Your body will attract scavengers. Should I bury you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "1c497341-c335-3207-939e-18bec947a7f8"], "hd0bf5caagccfcg4d3eg81bbg51b0e2d79de1": ["Let them come...", "f35c29c6-d643-8423-1c50-577ac06ee5de", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "35f73b11-4597-6a71-5bfd-076a7a0c5a82"], "he76df9aegd0adg4277g9cc2g9585b7994b3a": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "f9ce7fb9-ea5a-d1d8-1f1c-3775ec0f3e5d"], "hcaf1ebd5g38dbg4d51ga721g0fb669640aac": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "b81e715b-0c0e-471c-c37b-033837971e59"], "h34f10d1eg34dcg4a14ga070ge75f36839618": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Crash\\CRA_DeadPrisoner_Dead.html", "08bd8fb4-ecc2-8044-4ef3-5fa89265b35d"]}